{
  "texts": [
    "We compare them to their base judges, fine-tuning them, an order of magnitude larger judge, and specialized judges.",
    "We experiment with 4 datasets.",
    "The first two provide absolute ratings for language quality and are widely adopted in the LLM evaluation literature.",
    "The last two are synthetic datasets that focus on relative comparison, testing robustness to adversarial scenarios and scalability.",
    "Our dataset selection ensures that we test on both calibrated human judgments and challenging synthetic ground truth."
  ]
}